org.barghos.math.api.vector

Interface IVec4W

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.barghos.core.api.tuple.ITup4fW, org.barghos.core.api.tuple.ITupfW
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Vec4f

    public interface IVec4W
extends org.barghos.core.api.tuple.ITup4fW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 4-dimensional float vector.
